  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nIf receive PN for reply or mention in group / public chat and tap it to be redirected to that chat, then the notification in Activity center will still remain.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nActivity center notifications are deleted if the mention or reply has already been viewed in the chat view, no matter how the chat was opened.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/132359745-d6cb0f79-98f8-43d5-8cdc-7a018ea04970.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n**_Device1:_**\r\n1. Enable PNs on Android device\r\n2. Join group / community\r\n3. Put the app in the background\r\n\r\n**_Device 2:_** send a message replying or mentioning Device1\r\n\r\n**_Device 1:_** \r\n\r\n4. Tap the PN\r\n5. Navigate to the home screen and check Activity center\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 7/09\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
